title: Black Code
description: Café expresso, com grãos 100% arábica da Orfeu. Apresenta notas florais, frutadas e de caramelo.

title: White Code
description: A mocha, also known as a cafe mocha or caffè mocha, is a coffee drink made with chocolate, espresso, and milk.

title: Croissant Simples
description: A croissant is a laminated, yeast-leavened bakery product that contains dough/roll-in fat layers to create a flaky, crispy texture.

title: Sweet Chill
description: A matcha latte is a tea latte made with green tea powder and steamed milk. Matcha replaces the espresso in a traditional cafe latte, giving it a brilliant green color and lightly bitter flavor.

title: Green Code
description: A matcha latte is a tea latte made with green tea powder and steamed milk. Matcha replaces the espresso in a traditional cafe latte, giving it a brilliant green color and lightly bitter flavor.
